latestIgtvVideos.title: The Park Chennai - An Urban Haven
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
THE PARK HOTELS
ANYTHING BUT ORDINARY. 

The Park Hotels is a unique collection of contemporary luxury boutique hotels in India.

@theparkchennai is located on Anna Salai in the heart of the business district of Tamil Nadu's vibrant capital. Hirsch Bedner Associates, Los Angeles have designed this hotel.
 
This elegant and luxurious 214-room five star deluxe hotel stands on the historic premises of the erstwhile Gemini Film Studios. The precincts that created larger than life heroes and heroines since the 1940s, have now been transformed to house the theatre of life in its private and public spaces.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Enrich Salon Greenrich Program.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Love and light to all !!
This December at Enrich, they have big rewards for small steps to love our planet . You can win as you care for yourself - and the Earth.

With Greenrich rewards,
- You can Join in reducing, reusing and recycling materials like old jeans, bed linen, sarees, and plastic bottles that you bring along to the salon and win reward points.

- You can also win up to 10X the reward points by spinning the Virtuous Cycle, on bills worth Rs. 3000 - every time you visit.

- Post photos & details of your effort to reduce, reuse & recycle, add #greenrichrewards and tag @enrichsalons and win reward points.

- Ace the Greenrich Sustainability Quiz on Enrich app and win reward points.

You can redeem these reward points for your premium beauty services and professional self-care products.
Be a part of this journey of loving the planet.
Download the app now to start winning - for yourself and the planet too.

The place. This spot. This serene slice of the world — Key Monastery 🧡

I still remember stumbling upon its pictures and feeling so drawn to it…
That moment kinda sealed the deal — Spiti had to happen❤️✨

And now, being here, I get it.
The stillness, the vastness, the peace — it’s unreal.✨
It’s one of those places that makes you slow down, look within, and just feel.

A little reminder to be kind to yourself, to breathe deeper, and to let the quiet in.
Just me, this view, and a heart full of calm. 🌿✨🧿
